Brien O. HILL, petitioner,
v.
ASSOCIATES FOR RENEWAL IN EDUCATION, INC. No. 18-7112. Supreme Court of the United States Feb. 19, 2019.

*1202Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the District of Columbia Circuit denied.

Justice KAVANAUGH took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
